{"tid":911794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南非漢遇劫頭插15cm長刀 自行踩單車求診","createTime":"2018-11-22T07:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T19:14:02.000Z","uid":166622,"like":267,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"196297bfcb89eeef5c32867763197c6a4a83bcd0","tid":911794,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"南非一名34歲的餐廳經理韋恩（Shaun Wayne），日前踩單車返工，但卻在路上遇到兩名劫匪，更遭到其中一人用刀攻擊，15厘米長的刀就這樣插在他的頭上。最令人驚訝的是，受了傷的韋恩還可以打走劫匪，自行踩單車到800米以外的診所，頭上插着一把刀地走進診所嚇壞了所有的人。<br />\n<br />\n據報，韋恩事發當天如常踩單車到位於開普敦附近斯特蘭德的餐廳工作，沒想到半途竟然遇上兩名劫匪，想搶走韋恩的單車，三人扭打了起來，韋恩最終打走劫匪，保住單車，但是混亂中頭部被插一刀，而且刀子就插在他的頭部左側。<br />\n<br />\n難以置信的是，韋恩居然在這種情況下，居然好像無事一樣，還自己踩單車到800米外的一間診所求救，當他靠近登記處時，還很有禮貌的詢問「你們這裏有醫生嗎？醫生有空嗎？」護士形容：「他當時超冷靜！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181122/_2018112212540393505.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181122%2F_2018112212540393505.jpg&h=a46731dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02afe1106a21a58c9debfe2042f5ea61fcc771d0","tid":911794,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:41:22.000Z","msg":"唔撚痛?"},{"pid":"2598854ee09e9256046717b6f45c1e17920a60c6","tid":911794,"uid":222907,"like":339,"dislike":23,"score":316,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qNKzHCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqNKzHCM.jpg&h=e023cdd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嚇鬼咩"},{"pid":"ac183b9a9de8d09ac597cbf7b0c7ba6edcf8cc0c","tid":911794,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:45:14.000Z","msg":"嚇撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e19ec218cdfdce8e3341a9d08ac678cf3a7870","tid":911794,"uid":134666,"like":97,"dislike":24,"score":73,"quote":{"pid":"2598854ee09e9256046717b6f45c1e17920a60c6","tid":911794,"uid":222907,"like":339,"dislike":23,"scor